VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'don\'t, then you\'ve simply got excellent taste in time pieces. Dry British humor from Q. Got to love that guy. So, beyond the subtitles and the well, the stepped on joke in the quality mode. Actually, I just overall I just kind of prefer the'

[04:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'turbo output here. Uh, just in terms of framing, camera movement, and the fact that our Bond there kind of looks a little bit more on the Michael Fastpenter side. My initial thoughts while testing out V3 fast was that, you know, since it retains so much of the'

[04:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'prompt coherence, uh, that it would make for a really good sketch pad to test out your prompts before bumping them up to, you know, V3 big daddy. That said, as I continued to AB again with the same prompts, I tended to start gravitating'

[04:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'towards the fast outputs. Uh, take for example this kind of Game and Thrones inspired scene. The scouts confirm it, your grace. The frost giants press further south than ever before. This changes everything.'

