VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Gumroad. The link for that is down below. It is 100% totally free, though, if you would like to leave a donation, it is always appreciated. Another interesting V3 finding, this one coming from Martin Nebelong. Uh, this one only'

[08:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'works in the V3 quality mode, but if you upload an image frame of a character against a green screen, um, and then give it the prompt instantly jump/cut on frame one, two, and then whatever you'

